WEBVTT

00:02:59.210 --> 00:03:03.124
is a mixture of sweet and bitter.

00:03:03.730 --> 00:03:05.672
And the reason why I'm telling you this

00:03:05.696 --> 00:03:08.119
is because I think
there's more and more people

00:03:08.143 --> 00:03:09.935
all around the world today

00:03:09.959 --> 00:03:12.824
who have similarly mixed emotions

00:03:12.848 --> 00:03:15.120
about the lands they come from.

00:03:15.144 --> 00:03:17.805
We love our native countries, yeah?

00:03:17.829 --> 00:03:19.029
How can we not?

00:03:19.053 --> 00:03:23.494
We feel attached to the people,
the culture, the land, the food.

00:03:23.518 --> 00:03:24.710
And yet at the same time,

00:03:24.734 --> 00:03:30.416
we feel increasingly frustrated
by its politics and politicians,